Bootstrapping pipeline IV

set.seed(210)

boot_dist &lt;- duke_forest |&gt;
  specify(price ~ area) |&gt;
  generate(reps = 1000, type = "bootstrap") |&gt;
  fit()

Visualize the bootstrap distribution

boot_dist |&gt;
  filter(term == "area") |&gt;
  ggplot(aes(x = estimate)) +
  geom_histogram(binwidth = 10)

